{
  "stem": "24814.2",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the old battlefield smell, the smell of something burned and dead and rained on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Dead flesh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we walked through the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We saw-- we were puzzled at first.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The-- we saw these remnants of the A-frame.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had A-frame huts that were about six feet high.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Earth floor.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were bodies piled up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A lot of them were burned or charred.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in some places they're just a frame of the hut left-- nothing left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And wherever the huts-- these burned huts-- had been, there were piles of blackened bodies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Contorted.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we found out what had happened from the-- Seemed that a detachment of German engineers from the TODT organization-- T-O-D-T, the Todt group-- that's the German word for death, appropriately.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the man named Todt, who was the head of the engineer group, had been-- told them to kill as many as they could before the Americans liberated the place.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Why, God knows.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't-- the excuse you hear from the Holocaust deniers was that they had to burn people for sanitary reasons or something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But there was no sanitation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was no anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They could hear the American tank guns we had down the road, the American machine guns, and they went on an orgy of killing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They couldn't serve their purpose or any other purpose, except killing for the sake of killing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So they locked these people up in these A-frame huts, and they threw gasoline on, and they set fire to it, and they burned them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They just roasted them alive in these huts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's the bodies that we were seeing, which you'll see the pictures of.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the guards had stood around with bayonets.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
